        <h1 class="text-center"> About <span class= "navbar-brand">History Explorer<span> </h1>
        <p>Changing the way people explore historical landmarks with <strong>History Explorer</strong>—a user-friendly platform designed to make the journey more engaging, organized, and informative.</p>
        <h3 class= "display-8">Key Features:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Create & Manage Content</strong>: Users can easily create accounts to add, edit, and manage historical landmarks and comments. Administrators can organize and oversee regions to maintain structure.</li>
            <li><strong>Interactive Map Integration</strong>: Find landmarks on an interactive map powered by Google Maps. Add and view locations by region, making it easier to discover and visit landmarks.</li>
            <li><strong>Engaging Community Forum</strong>: Connect with fellow enthusiasts in an organized forum. Share insights, ask questions, and discuss landmarks in an easy-to-navigate space.</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive & Organized</strong>: Whether you're discovering hidden gems or connecting with others, History Explorer helps you explore landmarks with integrated features like searchability, community interactions, and more.</li>
        </ul>
