    <hr class="my-4">

    <h2 class="text-center"> Meet the Creator </h2>
    <p>Hi, I’m Nadia! The inspiration behind this app came from my passion for history and a desire to make it accessible to everyone. As someone who has just started learning about the history of Minnesota in 2023, I have been fascinated by the stories behind historical landmarks, I wanted to create an easy way for people to learn about these places, whether they’re visiting in person or exploring from the comfort of their own home.

I believe history has the power to inspire, educate, and connect us across time and space. This app is my way of bringing important stories to life and making them more engaging and interactive for enthusiasts.

Every landmark in the app has its own unique story, and I’m excited to help you discover them. Whether you’re a history enthusiast, a traveler, or just curious about the past, this app is for you.

Thank you for being part of this journey—explore, learn, and contribute to the rich history that surrounds us!</p>
